last_episode_to_air.overview: Gun it! The finalists put the pedal to the metal building badass postapocalyptic escape vehicles fit to outrun zombies. Do they have the needed speed?

name: Metal Shop Masters
overview: A group of metal artists torch, cut and weld epic, badass creations from hardened steel. Only one will win a $50,000 prize.

episodes.name: Test Your Metal
episodes.overview: The competition heats up fast as the artists create expressive, kinetic avatars that show off their skills. But two welders face immediate setbacks.

episodes.name: Getting Fishy
episodes.overview: Let's get cooking! Grillable form meets ingenious function when the contestants team up to torch and cut smokin' yet serviceable all-metal barbecues.

episodes.name: Lost in the Sauce
episodes.overview: Time to get scrappy. The welders put their engineering abilities to the test with mobiles made of unconventional materials like utensils and razors.

episodes.name: The Sound of Music
episodes.overview: The artists hope to strike a chord with one-of-a-kind music makers utilizing random instruments and metal. But can these offbeat twosomes get in sync?

episodes.name: A Shadow of a Doubt
episodes.overview: The semifinalists emerge from the shadows after welding square tubing, rod and sheet metal into artwork that tells two tales with sculpture and light.
